ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectLoran-C Stations St. Marys 1980 Termination of Treaty (US) #10
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America constituting an Agreement renewing the Agreement of March 29, 1977 concerning the Establishment of Mini Loran-C Stations in the vicinity of St. Marys River in Ontario and Michigan, done on 28 October and 5 December 1980.
